00:36:49.450 --> 00:36:53.500
And interface describes
how you interact

00:36:53.500 --> 00:36:57.460
with the information that's
being presented to you,

00:36:57.460 --> 00:37:01.030
and can greatly influence how
you interpret the information

00:37:01.030 --> 00:37:03.250
that is presented to you.

00:37:03.250 --> 00:37:07.630
They use, as an
example, I think it

00:37:07.630 --> 00:37:10.840
was like a Java applet,
the word synonym finder,

00:37:10.840 --> 00:37:13.210
this visual synonym finder.

00:37:13.210 --> 00:37:16.090
I actually have a memory
