00:37:16.090 --> 00:37:19.330
in the day, the
early internet days,

00:37:19.330 --> 00:37:21.790
of having it in this
bubble on the screen.

00:37:24.400 --> 00:37:28.060
PROFESSOR: Early
world wide web base.

00:37:28.060 --> 00:37:30.120
Internet is, you weren't around.

00:37:30.120 --> 00:37:32.040
AUDIENCE: No, that's true.

00:37:32.040 --> 00:37:34.870
That's what I meant.

00:37:34.870 --> 00:37:39.380
Back in the days when
dial-up was a thing.

00:37:39.380 --> 00:37:42.350
So I remembered that
experience, and so that was a--

00:37:45.440 --> 00:37:52.010
the way that they frame it is
that experience of seeing words

00:37:52.010 --> 00:37:53.608
and connection to
other words, and how

00:37:53.608 --> 00:37:56.150
they relate to each other, and
being able to make these hops,

00:37:56.150 --> 00:37:59.027
these may small hops, but end
up very far away from the word

00:37:59.027 --> 00:37:59.735
that you started.

00:37:59.735 --> 00:38:02.870
It makes language more
fluid, instead of like,

00:38:02.870 --> 00:38:05.690
when you read a dictionary,
which has basically the same

00:38:05.690 --> 00:38:10.070
information-- it contains
words and what they mean--

00:38:10.070 --> 00:38:13.940
but it's presented in this
