00:46:01.540 --> 00:46:06.480
And then we might be
less open to seeing where

00:46:06.480 --> 00:46:10.680
the users or the
participants actually

00:46:10.680 --> 00:46:13.950
subvert our
intentions, but still

00:46:13.950 --> 00:46:16.590
make interesting use
of the artifacts,

00:46:16.590 --> 00:46:19.260
and that is something
that we could actually

00:46:19.260 --> 00:46:24.615
benefit from, from allowing
and allowing ourselves to see.

00:46:27.180 --> 00:46:31.980
